        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "# 🌦️ Forecasting Weather Yogyakarta\r\n\r\n### AI-Powered Meteorological Prediction\r\n\r\nSistem prediksi cuaca berbasis **Deep Learning (LSTM)** yang dirancang untuk memantau kondisi atmosfer di wilayah Yogyakarta dan sekitarnya.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### 📊 Model Statistics\r\n- **Architecture**: Multi-layer LSTM (Long Short-Term Memory)\r\n- **Hardware**: NVIDIA GPU Accelerated (CUDA)\r\n- **Horizon**: 60-Day Future Forecast\r\n- **Parameters**: Temp, Humidity, Rain, Pressure (hPa)\r\n\r\n### 🔗 Open Source\r\n\r\n👉 [**GitHub Repository**](https://github.com/ernestoyoofi/forcasting-weather-yogyakarta)",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.4.1",
      "title": "Info",
      "type": "text"
